  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Bento Grid\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bento Grid\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-slate-50 flex overflow-hidden font-sans text-slate-900\\\">\\n  <!-- Sidebar Navigation -->\\n  <aside class=\\\"w-64 bg-slate-900 flex flex-col border-r border-slate-800\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"p-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-10\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-indigo-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white\\\">L</div>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white italic\\\">LedgerFlow</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <nav class=\\\"space-y-1\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 bg-slate-800 text-white rounded-lg\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-400\\\"></span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Dashboard</span>\\n        </a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg transition-colors\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600\\\"></span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Receipt History</span>\\n        </a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg transition-colors\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600\\\"></span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Monthly Reports</span>\\n        </a>\\n      </nav>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"mt-auto p-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl border border-slate-700\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2\\\">Database Sync</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-300\\\">Supabase Connected</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </aside>\\n\\n  <!-- Main Content Area -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col h-full overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- Top Header -->\\n    <header class=\\\"h-16 bg-white border-b border-slate-200 px-8 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800\\\">Financial Overview \342\200\224 October</h1>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors\\\">Export CSV</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors\\\">Sync Postgres</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </header>\\n\\n    <!-- Dashboard Grid -->\\n    <div class=\\\"p-6 grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-6 gap-4 flex-1 h-[calc(100%-4rem)]\\\">\\n      \\n      <!-- Summary Stats -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-1 bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Total Spending</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight\\\">$4,285.90</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-xs text-emerald-600 flex items-center gap-1 font-medium\\\">\\n          <span>\342\206\223 12% from last month</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-1 bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Total Receipts</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight\\\">42</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium\\\">Avg. $102.04 per entry</div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-1 bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Top Category</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight\\\">Business</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium\\\">38% of total spend</div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Quick Entry Form -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest mb-6\\\">New Receipt</h2>\\n        <form class=\\\"space-y-5\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <label class=\\\"block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2\\\">Vendor Name</label>\\n            <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"Amazon, Starbucks...\\\" class=\\\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 focus:border-indigo-500 transition-all\\\">\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\">\\n            <div>\\n              <label class=\\\"block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2\\\">Amount</label>\\n              <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"absolute left-4 top-3 text-slate-400 text-sm italic\\\">$</span>\\n                <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"0.00\\\" class=\\\"w-full pl-8 pr-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-sm\\\">\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div>\\n              <label class=\\\"block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2\\\">Date</label>\\n              <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"MM/DD/YY\\\" class=\\\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-sm\\\">\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div>\\n            <label class=\\\"block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2\\\">Category</label>\\n            <select class=\\\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-sm appearance-none\\\">\\n              <option>General</option>\\n              <option>Travel</option>\\n              <option>Food & Dining</option>\\n              <option>Office Supplies</option>\\n              <option>Technology</option>\\n            </select>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"pt-4\\\">\\n            <button type=\\\"button\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-900 text-white py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-sm shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-500/20 active:scale-95 transition-all\\\">Process Receipt</button>\\n          </div>\\n        </form>\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-auto p-4 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl border border-indigo-100\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-indigo-700 font-medium\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"font-bold\\\">Pro Tip:</span> In next update, you\'ll be able to drag & drop images for OCR processing.\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Spending Graph Area (Mockup) -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-9 row-span-2 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6\\\">\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Category Breakdown</h2>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500\\\"></div><span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-medium text-slate-500\\\">Food</span></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-sky-400\\\"></div><span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-medium text-slate-500\\\">Business</span></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-400\\\"></div><span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-medium text-slate-500\\\">Travel</span></div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-end gap-2 h-24\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-indigo-100 rounded-t-lg relative group h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-indigo-500 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 65%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-slate-300 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 45%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-sky-100 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-sky-400 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 80%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-slate-300 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 30%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-amber-100 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-amber-400 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 55%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-slate-300 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 40%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-indigo-100 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-indigo-500 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 90%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-slate-300 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 25%\\\"></div></div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Recent Transactions Table -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-9 row-span-3 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"px-6 py-4 border-b border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n           <h2 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Recent Ledger Entries</h2>\\n           <span class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 italic\\\">Showing 5 of 42 entries</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <table class=\\\"w-full text-left\\\">\\n            <thead>\\n              <tr class=\\\"bg-slate-50 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-bold\\\">\\n                <th class=\\\"px-6 py-3\\\">Date</th>\\n                <th class=\\\"px-6 py-3\\\">Vendor</th>\\n                <th class=\\\"px-6 py-3\\\">Category</th>\\n                <th class=\\\"px-6 py-3\\\">Status</th>\\n                <th class=\\\"px-6 py-3 text-right\\\">Amount</th>\\n              </tr>\\n            </thead>\\n            <tbody class=\\\"text-sm divide-y divide-slate-100\\\">\\n              <tr class=\\\"hover:bg-slate-50/80 transition-colors\\\">\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-medium text-slate-600\\\">Oct 24, 2023</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Apple Store</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full uppercase\\\">Technology</span></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-emerald-600 font-medium\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\\\"></div>Synced</div></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 text-right font-bold text-slate-900\\\">$1,299.00</td>\\n              </tr>\\n              <tr class=\\\"hover:bg-slate-50/80 transition-colors\\\">\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-medium text-slate-600\\\">Oct 22, 2023</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Fresh Market</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full uppercase\\\">Food</span></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-emerald-600 font-medium\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\\\"></div>Synced</div></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 text-right font-bold text-slate-900\\\">$84.50</td>\\n              </tr>\\n              <tr class=\\\"hover:bg-slate-50/80 transition-colors\\\">\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-medium text-slate-600\\\">Oct 21, 2023</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Shell Gas</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full uppercase\\\">Travel</span></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-slate-400 font-medium\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-300\\\"></div>Pending</div></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 text-right font-bold text-slate-900\\\">$52.18</td>\\n              </tr>\\n              <tr class=\\\"hover:bg-slate-50/80 transition-colors\\\">\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-medium text-slate-600\\\">Oct 20, 2023</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Amazon</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full uppercase\\\">Office</span></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-emerald-600 font-medium\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\\\"></div>Synced</div></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 text-right font-bold text-slate-900\\\">$12.99</td>\\n              </tr>\\n            </tbody>\\n          </table>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Bento Grid\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Bento Grid\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-slate-50 flex overflow-hidden font-sans text-slate-900\\\">\\n  <!-- Sidebar Navigation -->\\n  <aside class=\\\"w-64 bg-slate-900 flex flex-col border-r border-slate-800\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"p-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-10\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"w-8 h-8 bg-indigo-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-white\\\">L</div>\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white italic\\\">LedgerFlow</span>\\n      </div>\\n      <nav class=\\\"space-y-1\\\">\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 bg-slate-800 text-white rounded-lg\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-indigo-400\\\"></span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Dashboard</span>\\n        </a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg transition-colors\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600\\\"></span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Receipt History</span>\\n        </a>\\n        <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-3 text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-slate-800/50 rounded-lg transition-colors\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-600\\\"></span>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-sm font-medium\\\">Monthly Reports</span>\\n        </a>\\n      </nav>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"mt-auto p-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-slate-800/50 rounded-xl border border-slate-700\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-2\\\">Database Sync</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-2\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse\\\"></div>\\n          <span class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-300\\\">Supabase Connected</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </div>\\n  </aside>\\n\\n  <!-- Main Content Area -->\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 flex flex-col h-full overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <!-- Top Header -->\\n    <header class=\\\"h-16 bg-white border-b border-slate-200 px-8 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n      <h1 class=\\\"text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800\\\">Financial Overview \342\200\224 October</h1>\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-4\\\">\\n        <button class=\\\"px-4 py-2 bg-white border border-slate-200 text-slate-700 text-sm font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors\\\">Export CSV</button>\\n        <button class=\\\"px-4 py-2 bg-indigo-600 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg shadow-sm hover:bg-indigo-700 transition-colors\\\">Sync Postgres</button>\\n      </div>\\n    </header>\\n\\n    <!-- Dashboard Grid -->\\n    <div class=\\\"p-6 grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-6 gap-4 flex-1 h-[calc(100%-4rem)]\\\">\\n      \\n      <!-- Summary Stats -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-1 bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Total Spending</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight\\\">$4,285.90</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-xs text-emerald-600 flex items-center gap-1 font-medium\\\">\\n          <span>\342\206\223 12% from last month</span>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-1 bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Total Receipts</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight\\\">42</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium\\\">Avg. $102.04 per entry</div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-1 bg-white p-5 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col justify-between\\\">\\n        <span class=\\\"text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wider\\\">Top Category</span>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 tracking-tight\\\">Business</div>\\n        <div class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium\\\">38% of total spend</div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Quick Entry Form -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-3 row-span-6 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <h2 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest mb-6\\\">New Receipt</h2>\\n        <form class=\\\"space-y-5\\\">\\n          <div>\\n            <label class=\\\"block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2\\\">Vendor Name</label>\\n            <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"Amazon, Starbucks...\\\" class=\\\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-sm focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-indigo-500/20 focus:border-indigo-500 transition-all\\\">\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\">\\n            <div>\\n              <label class=\\\"block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2\\\">Amount</label>\\n              <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n                <span class=\\\"absolute left-4 top-3 text-slate-400 text-sm italic\\\">$</span>\\n                <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"0.00\\\" class=\\\"w-full pl-8 pr-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-sm\\\">\\n              </div>\\n            </div>\\n            <div>\\n              <label class=\\\"block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2\\\">Date</label>\\n              <input type=\\\"text\\\" placeholder=\\\"MM/DD/YY\\\" class=\\\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-sm\\\">\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n          <div>\\n            <label class=\\\"block text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase mb-2\\\">Category</label>\\n            <select class=\\\"w-full px-4 py-3 bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl text-sm appearance-none\\\">\\n              <option>General</option>\\n              <option>Travel</option>\\n              <option>Food & Dining</option>\\n              <option>Office Supplies</option>\\n              <option>Technology</option>\\n            </select>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"pt-4\\\">\\n            <button type=\\\"button\\\" class=\\\"w-full bg-slate-900 text-white py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-sm shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-500/20 active:scale-95 transition-all\\\">Process Receipt</button>\\n          </div>\\n        </form>\\n        <div class=\\\"mt-auto p-4 bg-indigo-50 rounded-xl border border-indigo-100\\\">\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[11px] leading-relaxed text-indigo-700 font-medium\\\">\\n            <span class=\\\"font-bold\\\">Pro Tip:</span> In next update, you\'ll be able to drag & drop images for OCR processing.\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Spending Graph Area (Mockup) -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-9 row-span-2 bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-center justify-between mb-6\\\">\\n          <h2 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Category Breakdown</h2>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex gap-4\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-indigo-500\\\"></div><span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-medium text-slate-500\\\">Food</span></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-sky-400\\\"></div><span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-medium text-slate-500\\\">Business</span></div>\\n            <div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5\\\"><div class=\\\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-400\\\"></div><span class=\\\"text-[10px] font-medium text-slate-500\\\">Travel</span></div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex items-end gap-2 h-24\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-indigo-100 rounded-t-lg relative group h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-indigo-500 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 65%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-slate-300 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 45%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-sky-100 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-sky-400 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 80%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-slate-300 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 30%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-amber-100 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-amber-400 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 55%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-slate-300 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 40%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-indigo-100 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-indigo-500 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 90%\\\"></div></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex-1 bg-slate-50 rounded-t-lg relative h-full\\\"><div class=\\\"absolute bottom-0 w-full bg-slate-300 rounded-t-lg\\\" style=\\\"height: 25%\\\"></div></div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <!-- Recent Transactions Table -->\\n      <div class=\\\"col-span-9 row-span-3 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 shadow-sm overflow-hidden flex flex-col\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"px-6 py-4 border-b border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-between\\\">\\n           <h2 class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-slate-900 uppercase tracking-widest\\\">Recent Ledger Entries</h2>\\n           <span class=\\\"text-xs text-slate-400 italic\\\">Showing 5 of 42 entries</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"flex-1 overflow-hidden\\\">\\n          <table class=\\\"w-full text-left\\\">\\n            <thead>\\n              <tr class=\\\"bg-slate-50 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 font-bold\\\">\\n                <th class=\\\"px-6 py-3\\\">Date</th>\\n                <th class=\\\"px-6 py-3\\\">Vendor</th>\\n                <th class=\\\"px-6 py-3\\\">Category</th>\\n                <th class=\\\"px-6 py-3\\\">Status</th>\\n                <th class=\\\"px-6 py-3 text-right\\\">Amount</th>\\n              </tr>\\n            </thead>\\n            <tbody class=\\\"text-sm divide-y divide-slate-100\\\">\\n              <tr class=\\\"hover:bg-slate-50/80 transition-colors\\\">\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-medium text-slate-600\\\">Oct 24, 2023</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Apple Store</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-sky-100 text-sky-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full uppercase\\\">Technology</span></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-emerald-600 font-medium\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\\\"></div>Synced</div></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 text-right font-bold text-slate-900\\\">$1,299.00</td>\\n              </tr>\\n              <tr class=\\\"hover:bg-slate-50/80 transition-colors\\\">\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-medium text-slate-600\\\">Oct 22, 2023</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Fresh Market</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full uppercase\\\">Food</span></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-emerald-600 font-medium\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\\\"></div>Synced</div></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 text-right font-bold text-slate-900\\\">$84.50</td>\\n              </tr>\\n              <tr class=\\\"hover:bg-slate-50/80 transition-colors\\\">\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-medium text-slate-600\\\">Oct 21, 2023</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Shell Gas</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full uppercase\\\">Travel</span></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-slate-400 font-medium\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-slate-300\\\"></div>Pending</div></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 text-right font-bold text-slate-900\\\">$52.18</td>\\n              </tr>\\n              <tr class=\\\"hover:bg-slate-50/80 transition-colors\\\">\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-medium text-slate-600\\\">Oct 20, 2023</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 font-bold text-slate-900\\\">Amazon</td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><span class=\\\"px-2 py-1 bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 text-[10px] font-bold rounded-full uppercase\\\">Office</span></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4\\\"><div class=\\\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-emerald-600 font-medium\\\"><div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-emerald-500\\\"></div>Synced</div></td>\\n                <td class=\\\"px-6 py-4 text-right font-bold text-slate-900\\\">$12.99</td>\\n              </tr>\\n            </tbody>\\n          </table>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n    </div>\\n  </main>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
